OL,3,CPlumber's community interest company
OL,4,Cmisled donors
OL,6,FA company run by a plumber previously
OL,7,Fhailed a hero for helping vulnerable
OL,8,Fcustomers misled donors and engaged in
OL,9,F"controversial fundraising", a
OL,10,Fregulator has found.
OL,12,FJames Anderson, a plumber from
OL,13,FBurnley, founded community interest
OL,14,Fcompany (CIC) Depher and rose to
OL,15,Finternet fame for fixing in-need
OL,16,Fcustomers' boilers for free.
