OL,4,Cmisled donors
OL,6,FActor Hugh Grant was previously
OL,7,Freported to have donated tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds to the company,
OL,9,Fwhich had pledged to help elderly
OL,10,Fpeople and those in financial need
OL,11,Fwith free plumbing tasks.
OL,13,FIn 2022, an elderly couple given a new
OL,14,Fboiler for free likened Mr Anderson to
OL,15,Fan "angel in disguise".
