OL,3,CPlumber's community interest company
OL,4,Cmisled donors
OL,6,FBut, last year, a BBC investigation
OL,7,Fsaw the organisation accused of faking
OL,8,Fstories of good deeds to raise
OL,9,Fmillions of pounds, with the
OL,10,Fbroadcaster saying the CIC had used
OL,11,Fimages of vulnerable people without
OL,12,Ftheir consent and faked stories about
OL,13,Facts of kindness.
