OL,3,CPlumber's community interest company
OL,4,Cmisled donors
OL,6,FIn response to that investigation, Mr
OL,7,FAnderson said he "held (his) hands up"
OL,8,Fabout mistakes made by the company,
OL,9,Fbut added that he had complained to
OL,10,Fthe communications regulator Ofcom
OL,11,Fover the broadcaster's investigation,
OL,12,Fclaiming online trolls had "doctored"
OL,13,Fimages and that he was being "set up
OL,14,Fin a witch hunt".
OL,16,FNow an investigation into Depher by
OL,17,Fthe Fundraising Regulator has found
OL,18,Fmultiple breaches of the code of
OL,19,Ffundraising practice, including around
OL,20,Finforming donors and treating people
OL,21,Ffairly.
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@fO]tD@\OUtD@eO]uD@^OUvD@PO]
