OL,3,CPlumber's community interest company
OL,4,Cmisled donors
OL,6,FThe findings, published on Wednesday,
OL,7,Fincluded that there had been
OL,8,Fmisleading use of images on social
OL,9,Fmedia, with pictures of the same
OL,10,Fpeople alongside different stories, as
OL,11,Fwell as an inability of the CIC, on
OL,12,Fmultiple occasions, to "evidence
OL,13,Fclaims made as part of its fundraising
OL,14,Fefforts".
OL,16,FThere was also said to be
OL,17,F"controversial fundraising", with
OL,18,F"frequent reference to potential death
OL,19,For death from suicide in its
OL,20,Fmaterials".
OL,26,@tD@XOUvD@HO]yD@AOUyD@[O]zD@AOU|D@JO]
