OL,6,FThe purpose of donations raised for
OL,7,Fthe organisation was also deemed
OL,8,F"inconsistent", with some suggested to
OL,9,Fbe for a specific purpose and others
OL,10,Ffor general use by the CIC.
OL,12,FThe Fundraising Regulator noted that
OL,13,Fdonations to the organisation had been
OL,14,Fused to buy a house but said decisions
OL,15,Faround how money is used lies with a
OL,16,Fdifferent regulator.
