OL,6,FThe CIC Regulator, which the
OL,7,FFundraising Regulator is sharing its
OL,8,Ffindings with, said it had noted the
OL,9,Ffindings but would not confirm whether
OL,10,Fit was carrying out its own
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FA spokesperson said: "Any complaints
OL,14,Fregarding CICs are taken seriously and
OL,15,Fif a breach in CIC legislation is
OL,16,Fidentified, then appropriate
OL,17,Fregulatory action will be considered.
