OL,6,F"The regulator would expect all CICs
OL,7,Fto comply with any legal obligations
OL,8,For regulations to which they are
OL,9,Fsubject whilst they deliver benefit to
OL,10,Fthe communities they serve."
OL,12,FDepher had applied three times to the
OL,13,FCharity Commission to be registered as
OL,14,Fa charity but was rejected for having
OL,15,Ffailed to demonstrate that it met the
OL,16,Fnecessary legal criteria set out by
OL,17,Fcharity law.
